{
  "texts": [
    "Once deployed, they can perform continuous, real-time evaluations with minimal operational cost.",
    "Moreover, their scalability allows rapid testing across multiple products or batches, which is particularly valuable in quality control and high-throughput screening environments.",
    "Despite these strengths, AI-driven systems also have limitations.",
    "Their performance heavily depends on the quality and diversity of the training dataset.",
    "In unfamiliar conditions or with novel compounds not represented in the data, prediction accuracy may decline."
  ]
}